otlin (Android), bridged to React Native, that runs Vision framework inference entirely on-device. Completely offline, completely private.\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h2,{children:\"Privacy Model\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.p,{children:\"No accounts. No cloud sync. No analytics. SwipeSpark accesses the device media library through the standard Expo permissions API and never transmits photo data anywhere. Everything stays on your device.\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(e.h2,{children:\"What I Learned\"}),`\n`,(0,n.jsxs)(e.ul,{children:[`\n`,(0,n.jsxs)(e.li,{children:[(0,n.jsx)(e.strong,{children:\"Expo Router\"}),\" has matured into a genuinely production-ready framework. Tab navigation, deep linking, and modal sheets all work exactly as you'd expect on both platforms.\"]}),`\n`,(0,n.jsxs)(e.li,{children:[(0,n.jsx)(e.strong,{children:\"App Store review\"}),\" is slower than Play Store by roughly 2\\u20133x. Plan accordingly.\"]}),`\n`,(0,n.jsxs)(e.li,{children:[(0,n.jsx)(e.strong,{children:\"Native modules\"}),\" are less painful than their reputation suggests \\u2014 the main cost is setting up the bridge; the actual native code is straightforward.\"]}),`\n`]}),`\n`,(0,n.jsx)(i,{items:[{label:\"Platforms\",value:\"iOS + Android\"},{label:\"Gestures\",value:\"60 fps\"},{label:\"Cloud data\",value:\"Zero\"}]})]})}function p(t={}){let{wrapper:e}=t.components||{};return e?(0,n.jsx)(e,{...t,children:(0,n.jsx)(c,{...t})}):c(t)}function h(t,e){throw new Error(\"Expected \"+(e?\"component\":\"object\")+\" `\"+t+\"` to be defined: you likely forgot to import, pass, or provide it.\")}return b(k);})();\n;return Component;"